Subject: [PATCH 1196/2241] fix: arm64: defconfig: stop ignoring possible el1
 async abort errors
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

This patch disables CONFIG_IGNORE_ASYNC_ABORT which was added
to ignore asynchronous external abort in EL1.

The EL1 asynchronous external abort happened when a PCIe switch
with no endpoint was connected to the PCIe slot.

Masking EL1 errors might hide other existing issues and itâ€™s not
the correct way to handles such cases.

